  <brief_title>Evaluation of Buffer on Immune Response to Oral Polio Vaccine (OPV) in Bangladesh</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Effect of Buffer on the Immune Response to Oral Poliovirus Vaccine in Bangladesh: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
