  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis:

      The immunogenicity of oral polio vaccine (OPV) will be enhanced in Bangladeshi infants who
      receive bicarbonate buffer at the time of polio immunization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will conduct a study to evaluate the impact of administering bicarbonate
      buffer on the serologic responses to oral polio vaccine (OPV) in Bangladeshi infants.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
